Challenge was to find if the number is a power of four without loops and recursion
class Solution {
    public boolean isPowerOfFour(int num) {
       if(num == 0) 
        return false; 
    return Math.floor(Math.log(num) / Math.log(4))==Math.ceil(Math.log(num) / Math.log(4));  
    }
}
#Status: Solved
